Company Overview of Allen Investment Management, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Allen Investment Management, LLC is a holding company. Through its subsidiaries, the firm provides separate client focused portfolios and hedge funds. It primarily provides its services to pooled investment vehicles. The firm also caters to high net worth individuals. The firm is based in New York, New York. Allen Investment Management, LLC operates as a subsidiary of Allen & Company, Inc.


