Team > Allen Williamson


Allen Williamson

Senior Relationship Manager


Allen Williamson joined Chiron Investment Management, LLC as a Managing Director, Senior Relationship Manager.  He was previously head of the Private Wealth Group for Guggenheim Investments, which was dedicated to serving Private Wealth advisors at select firms and work exclusively with high net worth and ultra high net worth clientele.  understanding of high net worth advisors and investors. He joined Guggenheim Investments in 2009.  Prior to Guggenheim Investments, Mr. Williamson served as group president of Nuveen Investments’ Managed Assets Group, where he developed and led a consultative-based, multi-disciplined product and services platform and built wealth management. Mr. Williamson earned a B.A. in international studies from the University of South Carolina, a Certified Investment Management Analyst  (CIMA®) designation and a Certificate in Alternative Investments from the Wharton School at the University of Pennsylvania.  He is series 7, 24, and 66 registered.


























